-Kit-

The otter bot hears gun fire, and she grins. Finally, a battle! After nearly blowing the head off that Nemisis Guy, she found that it was quite fun!

Kit arrives in a matter of minutes, and looks out of the bushes, seeing a fairly small, but fierce battle on. She leaps out and pulls out her gun, firing one at Zergling and one at Zardus, knowing the other 2 were Maximals!
